.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# IDE
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo

# Misc
*.bak
demo/
ClawPanel_logo/

# Local agent/tooling notes (keep local only)
local/
local-binaries/
CLAUDE.md
Claude.md

